rows.label: qst102708_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, you're here.
What are the patient's symptoms?

rows.label: qst102708_msg0002
rows.name: A Man-Eater?

rows.label: qst102708_msg0003
rows.name: Fusion of man and Blade...

rows.label: qst102708_msg0004
rows.name: Interesting. I'll help you.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0005
rows.name:
Saw some old records about them
when I was a military doctor.
Didn't know they were really out there.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0007
rows.name:
Where's the patient?
...Invidia?

rows.label: qst102708_msg0008
rows.name:
I was with the Superbian military.
Can't go there.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0009
rows.name: Still, if he's half human...

rows.label: qst102708_msg0010
rows.name:
You take care of the Blade side there.
I'll deal with the human half.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0011
rows.name:
Details can wait.
I'll make a medicine.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0012
rows.name:
I need three Gloomwood Roots...
one crystal of Cloud Sea Halite...
Oh, and one more thing.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0013
rows.name:
Gotta have some kind of vegetable.
One that makes you feel younger
just by eating it.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0014
rows.name:
You'll find the first two ingredients in
Spirit Crucible Elpys and the Cliffs
of Mors.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0015
rows.name:
Don't know where to find that
vegetable, though. Try asking my
assistant.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0101
rows.name: Roots... Roots...

rows.label: qst102708_msg0201
rows.name: Very good.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0202
rows.name: Just one more thing I need now.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0203
rows.name: Dragon Incense.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0204
rows.name:
But from the symptoms you mentioned,
the normal stuff won't cut it.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0205
rows.name:
Got to be the pure stuff.
True Dragon Incense from Invidia.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0206
rows.name: Go get some for me.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0207
rows.name:
True Dragon Incense comes from the
Dragon's Stomach in Invidia.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0208
rows.name:
For a single adult male...
two samples should do.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0209
rows.name: Bring it quick, for the patient's sake.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0301
rows.name:
What's Dragon Incense?
Assistant!

rows.label: qst102708_msg0302
rows.name: There. Ask him.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0401
rows.name:
True Dragon Incense...
Indeed.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0402
rows.name:
Got to make an infusion, boil with
the other ingredients and stir for
three straight days and nights.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0403
rows.name: ...I'd probably fall asleep.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0404
rows.name:
Assistant has other work to do, too.
Can't attend to this constantly.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0405
rows.name:
Your friends will help?
Perfect.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0501
rows.name:
Man-Eaters...
Fusions of man and Blade...

rows.label: qst102708_msg0502
rows.name: Just like me and roots.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0601
rows.name:
Medicine's all finished.
Very high quality.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0602
rows.name:
Contains special ethocrines to improve
the body's circulatory efficiency.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0603
rows.name:
Ought to trigger tissue restoration
once the Blade power has been
normalized and... Hmm.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0604
rows.name:
You know what? Too hard to explain.
Just make him drink this and do your
Blade fixing.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0605
rows.name:
Won't be perfect, though.
Nothing is.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0606
rows.name:
He'll still die eventually.
He's only human.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0607
rows.name: Now hurry on back to the patient.

rows.label: qst102708_msg0701
rows.name: I love a job well done.
